938	\begin{proof}
939	  \leanok
940	  Compose iter-033's $\HModulePrimeTopLinearEquiv$ (which lands on $\Ext_u\,X_2\,F\,n$ for $X_2 = (\constantSheaf\,J\,\_).\mathrm{obj}\,(\ModuleCat.\mathrm{of}\,k\,k)$) with the universe-bump $\Ext.\mathtt{chgUnivLinearEquiv}$ from Definition~\ref{def:Abelian_Ext_chgUnivLinearEquiv} (which lifts $\Ext_u\,X_2\,F\,n$ to $\Ext_{u+1}\,X_2\,F\,n$). By definition (iter-009), $\HModule\,k\,F\,n = \Ext_{u+1}\,X_2\,F\,n$, so the composition yields the desired $\LinearEquiv$. Plan-agent $\mathtt{lean\_run\_code}$ probe (iter-034 pass) confirms the one-liner $(\HModulePrimeTopLinearEquiv\,k\,F\,n\,h_T).\mathtt{trans}\,\Ext.\mathtt{chgUnivLinearEquiv}$ typechecks and produces kernel-only axioms. Both $\HasExt_u$ and $\HasExt_{u+1}$ must be passed as explicit hypotheses (typeclass synthesis from $\HasSheafify$ alone times out on the underlying $\HasSmallLocalizedHom$ chain at 20\,000 heartbeats).
